Location

Alabata, Abeokuta

The Location

Abeokuta is a city located in southwestern Nigeria and the capital of Ogun State. Abeokuta's location is strategic, as it is situated close to Lagos, one of Nigeria's major economic hubs. Being in proximity to Lagos can bring potential economic benefits and growth opportunities to the city, making it an attractive location for investors. It is a potentially good choice for land investment.
